high_descs: Turn around and move to the sink next to the dishwasher.
Pick up the fork in the sink to the right of the tomato.
Open the cabinet door underneath the sink and next to the dishwasher. Place the fork in the mug in the cabinet.
Pick up the mug in the cabinet underneath the sink and close the cabinet door.
Turn right and move toward the counter with the pencil on top of it and then turn left and face the area of the counter to the right of the dishwasher.
Set the mug with the fork in it down on the edge of the kitchen counter slightly right of the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a fork in it on the kitchen counter.

high_descs: Pick up the fork from the sink.
Open up the cabinet under the sink and put the fork in the mug under the sink.
Pick up the mug from under the sink.
Bring the mug to the counter on the right.
Put the mug on the counter above the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with fork on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and heads towards the sink.
Pick up the fork inside the sink.
Open the right cabinet door below the sink and place the fork in the cup inside the cabinet.
Pick the cup out of the cabinet and close the door.
Turn right and head towards the middle of the counter on your left.
Place the cup with the fork on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place the fork in a cup to put it on the counter.
